-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Nov 11, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vcm1665702739978.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vcm1665702739978.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vcm1665702739978.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vcm1665702739978\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">[LOGICALS]\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"vcm1665702739978___logicals__447484\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use the [LOGICALS] section of the assignment file to assign values to logicals that can be accessed using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$logical</span> ProcScript function. Each application can have its own set of logicals.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"vcm1665702739978__topic_d137504e1_d137505e1_d137506e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d859537e56\">Syntax</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vcm1665702739978__p_d137510e1_d137511e1_d137512e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">[LOGICALS]</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vcm1665702739978__p_d137513e1_d137514e1_d137515e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">LogicalName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vcm1665702739978__topic_d98002e1_d98003e1_d98004e1_d98005e1_d98006e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d859537e80\"> Arguments </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"vcm1665702739978__ul_ufl_xrd_vvb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vcm1665702739978__li_d48509e1_d48510e1_d48511e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">LogicalName</var>—logical name. It is not case-sensitive . The\n                  <var class=\"keyword varname\">LogicalName</var> may contain any characters except spaces, tabs, and\n               equal signs (=). </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vcm1665702739978__li_d48512e1_d48513e1_d48514e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>—value for the logical name. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vcm1665702739978__section_vfl_xrd_vvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d859537e104\">Example: Setting Logicals </h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example assignment file defines a logical named\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">work_directory</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"vcm1665702739978__pre_wfl_xrd_vvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[LOGICALS]\nwork_directory = c:/my_app/test/work</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n<p class=\"p\">For information about a 4GL <code class=\"ph codeph\">[LOGICALS]</code> example, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kyf1665702740049.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kyf1665702740049.html\" title=\"Return the value of an application logical.\">$logical</a>. </p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vcm1665702739978__topic_d98007e1_d98008e1_d98009e1_d98010e1_d98011e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d859537e135\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vcm1665702739978__p_d137528e1_d137529e1_d137530e1\">Uniface provides a number of logicals for configuring the Uniface IDE, the Web Application Server (WASV), SMTP authentication, and so on.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kyf1665702740049.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$logical</a><p>Return the value of an application logical.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532955\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532955\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "[LOGICALS] Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Nov 11, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 [LOGICALS] Use the [LOGICALS] section of the assignment file to assign values to logicals that can be accessed using the $logical ProcScript function. Each application can have its own set of logicals. Syntax [LOGICALS] LogicalName = Value Arguments LogicalName —logical name. It is not case-sensitive . The LogicalName may contain any characters except spaces, tabs, and equal signs (=). Value —value for the logical name. Example: Setting Logicals The following example assignment file defines a logical named work_directory : [LOGICALS] work_directory = c:/my_app/test/work Copy For information about a 4GL [LOGICALS] example, see $logical . Description Uniface provides a number of logicals for configuring the Uniface IDE, the Web Application Server (WASV), SMTP authentication, and so on. Related Links $logical Return the value of an application logical. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}